Product Slider Building Block

Building Block that allows you to create product sliders from picked products

Main Features:

  • Picked Products Slider
  • Website Editor Integration
  • Backend Configuration
  • Multiple Slider Options

Picked Products Slider

Promote your picked products easily with this responsive carousel slider.

Do not limit yourself to automated products generation and pick your favorite products individually to build a Featured Products, New Products or any other desired products slider just by picking any products you like.

Website Editor Integration

Very simple and intuitive usage with seamless integration with Odoo website editor.

Single slider can be used indefinite times on indefinite number of pages with same configuration or it can cloned and used with another configuration.

Backend Configuration

Each products slider is created and configured on backend, which means that once you dropped the slider(s) on website and made changed to configuration you wont need to re-drag&drop them again for configuration to take effect. All changes on backend will reflect on sliders in the website instantly after you save it.

Multiple Slider Options

Each slider can have configuration for:

  • Products per Slide

    Defines number of products per single slide.

  • Slide Interval

    The amount of time to delay between automatically cycling an item. If 0, carousel will not automatically cycle.

  • Pause on Hover

    Pauses the cycling of the carousel on mouseenter and resumes the cycling of the carousel on mouseleave.

  • Wrap

    Whether the carousel should cycle continuously or have hard stops.

Quality Check

Module passed following quality control checks

The Odoo Community Association pylint-odoo
